{"id":"d969d1f6-cd1e-4eef-86fd-d0eb8cc2b9ca","title":"1548/03: To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni","type":"main-list-block","children":[{"id":"1a7b5cd3-a114-44e7-a70b-ba0ada64a629","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"From Rome, [March ..., 1548].","standoffProperties":[{"id":"131d4289-08d8-4825-b23d-b9dff9e972b6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":3,"value":"8532f2fa-b614-4eed-9eae-586327f6a15a","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"1526911e-20a4-4748-8227-fa53b7361d5b","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":5,"end":8,"value":"501a8a32-2c8a-4934-9060-8c7e36339f0f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"d241a4bd-611b-43e2-b9de-676a076ac11c","type":"codex/time-reference","start":12,"end":26,"value":"9b2208c1-e540-4fad-a2ce-25ff5df9c719","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"9c9c7924-0c7f-4fe8-a47f-ecf04e6374aa","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"To Lionardo di Buonarroto Simoni,","standoffProperties":[{"id":"b32cad47-17b4-490b-b97b-72180260750d","type":"style/italics","start":0,"end":31,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"660f5da2-4027-4c53-982a-fb857cd5339c","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":31,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"0763b902-f969-4a64-a51b-52dd44a484f0","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"in Florence.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"17a24b92-25a0-476c-ab3b-8898ee1fc0df","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":1,"value":"0c663cc2-dd9f-40ce-b17b-734e41b369ef","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ef83e5b0-52c2-47e5-b760-a046d30f83a5","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":3,"end":10,"value":"671ee7e7-ae1b-4a5a-9591-b40203d5108f","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]}],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"2be646fb-4c42-4408-a7a4-ab5d55bd0314","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"","standoffProperties":[],"blockProperties":[]},{"id":"23cecfb9-723d-4889-a23f-a1d5c13e37d3","type":"standoff-editor-block","text":"Lionardo,\u00A0\u2014\u00A0I am glad that thou hast told me about this decree of banishment, for although I have in the\u00A0past avoided all conversation or dealings with [Florentine] exiles, I shall be still more careful for the future. As to that\u00A0time when I was ill in the house of Strozzi, I do not consider that I was then actually in their house, for I was in Messer Luigi del Riccio\u0027s room, who was my very great friend. Since Bartolomeo Angelini died I have not found anyone who was able to look after my affairs better than he did, nor have I found any more faithful. I have had nothing to do with the house since he died, and all Rome can bear\u00A0witness to this as well as to the life I live: for I keep\u00A0to myself, I go about little, and I speak to nobody\u00A0\u2014\u00A0least of all to Florentines. If a man salute me in the street I cannot do otherwise than answer him with fair words: then I pass on. If I could know which of them were exiles I would pass by with no reply whatever. As I have already said, I shall henceforth keep a strict watch over myself, especially as I have so many other things to think of that it is a burden\u00A0merely to maintain life itself. As to setting up shop, do as ye yourselves think good, for it is not my trade and I cannot advise you to any good purpose. I have only this warning to give you, that if ye waste the money already in your hands ye will never have it made good to you.","standoffProperties":[{"id":"da44c7d7-80c6-44b3-b343-1ac496a2ecb4","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":7,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"f4f4de0e-cf52-40d4-8804-3cda8cffe71a","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":7,"value":"93ce2119-f2b8-4642-b551-7b8ca6b1ed96","zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"ec308b36-563b-4e48-87e1-051b1011f7bd","type":"attitude/thanks","start":12,"end":217,"value":null,"zeroPoint":false,"metadata":[]},{"id":"62473954-349f-48c7-9eb1-83058b5f95bb","type":"codex/entity-reference